About the game:

It's survival of the 'biggest' in this action-packed deep-sea challenge. Eat your way to the top of the food chain and encounter deadly predators. You'll uncover breathtaking scenery in multiple subterranean environments as you fishtail your way through the blue abyss. Keep an eye out for power-ups, mermaids, and bonus stages. Have you got what it takes to defeat the Shark King? Swim into slippery fun and find out!
